Set of scripts to get you started with a fresh installation of OpenSuse, with nginx and mono running asp.net mvc 3 sites using the Razor view engine.

clone (https://github.com/erikzaadi/MonoRazorScripts.git) or download and unzip (https://github.com/erikzaadi/MonoRazorScripts/zipball/master) this repository and run 
sudo sh ./install.sh

See [BLOGPOST] for more details